**Standard Glass:**
```css
.glass {
  backdrop-filter: blur(12px) saturate(180%);
  background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);  /* Light mode */
  background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05); /* Dark mode */
  border: 1px solid rgba(148, 163, 184, 0.25);
