```

**Variations:**
- `.glass-strong` - More opaque, stronger blur (20px)
- `.glass-subtle` - Less blur (5px), very transparent
- `.glass-header` - Optimized for sticky headers (16px blur)
- `.glass-modal` - Heavy blur (24px), dark overlay
- `.glass-card` - Card variant with gradient background

