## ⚡ Animations & Transitions

### Performance Requirements

**CRITICAL: All animations MUST be GPU-accelerated (60fps minimum)**

**Safe properties (GPU-accelerated):**
- `transform` (translate, scale, rotate)
- `opacity`
- `filter` (blur, saturate)

**Unsafe properties (avoid in animations):**
- `width`, `height` (triggers layout)
- `top`, `left`, `margin`, `padding` (triggers layout)
- `color`, `background-color` (triggers paint)

### Timing Functions

```css
/* Standard easing */
cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1)  /* Default smooth easing */

/* Custom easing */
--ease-bounce: cubic-bezier(0.68, -0.55, 0.265, 1.55);
--ease-elastic: cubic-bezier(0.175, 0.885, 0.32, 1.275);
```

### Durations

```css
--duration-instant: 75ms;   /* Instant feedback (button press) */
--duration-fast: 150ms;     /* Fast interactions (hover) */
--duration-base: 200ms;     /* Default transitions */
--duration-medium: 300ms;   /* Modal open/close */
--duration-slow: 500ms;     /* Page transitions */
--duration-slower: 700ms;   /* Special effects */
```

### Component Animation Patterns

**Bento Card (Widget) Hover:**
```tsx
<motion.div
  initial={{ opacity: 0, y: 20 }}
  animate={{ opacity: 1, y: 0 }}
  exit={{ opacity: 0, y: -20 }}
  transition={{ duration: 0.4, ease: [0.4, 0, 0.2, 1] }}
  style={{ willChange: isHovered ? 'transform' : 'auto' }}
>
  {/* GPU-accelerated gradient glow */}
  <div
    className={`absolute inset-0 transition-opacity duration-300 ${isHovered ? 'opacity-100' : 'opacity-0'}`}
    style={{
      background: 'linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(233, 30, 140, 0.15), rgba(0, 201, 255, 0.15))',
      filter: 'blur(20px)',
      transform: 'translateZ(0)', // Force GPU acceleration
    }}
  />
</motion.div>
```

**Button Hover:**
```css
.hover-lift {
  transform: translateZ(0); /* GPU hint */
  transition: transform 200ms cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1),
              box-shadow 200ms cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);
}

.hover-lift:hover {
  transform: translateY(-4px) translateZ(0);
  box-shadow: var(--shadow-floating);
  will-change: transform, box-shadow;
}
```

