## 🚨 Common Mistakes to Avoid

### ❌ DON'T DO THIS

**Using random colors:**
```tsx
<div style={{ color: '#FF5733' }}> {/* ❌ Not in design system */}
```

**Animating layout properties:**
```css
.bad {
  transition: margin-top 200ms; /* ❌ Causes layout thrashing */
}
```

**Missing focus indicators:**
```css
button:focus {
  outline: none; /* ❌ Accessibility violation */
}
```

**Technical error messages:**
```tsx
{error && <p>Error: {error.code}</p>} {/* ❌ Not actionable */}
```

**Blank loading states:**
```tsx
{loading ? null : <Content />} {/* ❌ No feedback */}
```

### ✅ DO THIS INSTEAD

**Use design system colors:**
```tsx
<div className="text-magenta-700 dark:text-cyan-500">
```

**Animate with transform/opacity:**
```css
.good {
  transform: translateZ(0);
  transition: transform 200ms;
}
.good:hover {
  transform: translateY(-4px) translateZ(0);
}
```

**Visible focus indicators:**
```css
button:focus-visible {
  outline: 2px solid #E91E8C;
  outline-offset: 2px;
}
```

**Actionable error messages:**
```tsx
{error && (
  <div className="text-error-500">
    <p className="font-semibold">Could not save changes</p>
    <p className="text-sm">Check your browser settings and try again.</p>
  </div>
)}
```

**Skeleton loaders:**
```tsx
{loading ? (
  <div className="animate-pulse space-y-4">
    <div className="h-8 bg-slate-200 dark:bg-slate-700 rounded w-3/4"></div>
    <div className="h-4 bg-slate-200 dark:bg-slate-700 rounded"></div>
  </div>
) : (
  <Content />
)}
