## 🎓 Quick Tips

**When in doubt:**
1. Check existing components first (`src/components/`)
2. Reference Tailwind config (`config/tailwind.config.js`)
3. Test in both light and dark mode
4. Verify keyboard navigation works
5. Run `npm run build` to check bundle size

**For new components:**
1. Start with existing patterns (Widget, Modal, Button)
2. Use Tailwind utilities (avoid custom CSS)
3. Add TypeScript types for all props
4. Test performance (Lighthouse, React DevTools Profiler)
5. Document usage in comments

**For animations:**
1. Only animate `transform` and `opacity`
2. Use `will-change` sparingly
3. Add `transform: translateZ(0)` for GPU acceleration
4. Test on low-end devices (throttle CPU in DevTools)

